1. The bash script enables to find a file, make a copy of the file with new name taken input from user
2. It takes inpust for source-file to search for the file and input name for destination file to keep a copy there.
3. It works and can be accessed through a remote connection over ssh

The command for the remote connection has to be



ssh <remoteuser>@<ipaddress> 'bash -s' < <path to file/remote_accessCopy.sh>
